+
+Usage in RST files:
+
+    .. cilium-helm-install::
+       :namespace: kube-system
+       :set: image.pullPolicy=IfNotPresent
+             ipam.mode=kubernetes
+
+This will generate:
+- For stable: tabs showing both Helm Repository and OCI Registry options
+- For not stable: a simple helm install command
